*****************************************************************************

srus v0.2 // Simple Ruby URL Shortener
by Nikola Kantar (nkantar.com)

URL shortener written in Ruby (with the help of Sinatra and DataMapper).
Intended for personal use - not by multiple people.

Version history and feature wishlist below.

*****************************************************************************

To-do

- session-based auth
