- API

*****************************************************************************

Version 0.2

+ deleting links
+ custom 404
+ custom 500
+ design
+ click link in list to load in new tab
+ if no protocol, assume http

*****************************************************************************

Version 0.1 (Mon May 14 2012)

+ Link model
+ adding links
+ retrieving links
+ basic http auth for everything except retrieving

